PrecisRe-appointment of EVELYNE HENRY, of Cumberland, Ontario, as Deputy Chairperson of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of two years; and orders that EVELYNE HENRY shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective July 6, 2001.
